      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZATARA'S IMAGE (4) made light work of a wide draw last time with a slick early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing second (16.98) at this track over 300m. Key chance in this line up. COMMON CHAOS (7) rocketed out of the rails draw with a scorching early sectional and clocking 17.00 in a one length win at this track over 300m last time. Will go close again if runs up to latest. MAD HOWLER (5) has a strong record this trip with six wins and two placings from 13 starts. Scored by half a length last time (16.95) in a Grade 2/3 over 300m at this track. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. INVESTED (1) is always a threat when he races at this track and distance.",
